2008-**Counterfactual assumption disclosure as a first-class artifact.** The demo composes a one-paragraph disclosure per scenario. Production maintains an institutional library of approved disclosure templates per scenario type, per disease, and per evidence source, reviewed by the clinical communication team and updated whenever the underlying trial-derived priors change. The disclosure is rendered alongside every forecast surface and is non-removable.
